  <p>PAGCOR launched the 24-hour National Problem Gambling Helpline on Wednesday, May 26, 2026, the first round-the-clock service in the Philippines dedicated specifically to gambling-related problems. The line &mdash; reachable at (02) 8248-9568 &mdash; operates from a helpline office located within PAGCOR's corporate headquarters in Pasay City, staffed by 12 trained para-counselors working across three daily shifts.</p>

  <p>The NPGH is implemented by PAGCOR in partnership with Seagulls Flock Organization Inc. (SFO), a Philippine nonprofit that advocates for substance-use prevention, treatment and recovery, and for problem gambling and gaming support. SFO chairperson Teresita "Chit" Castillo, speaking at the launch, noted that the NPGH is the first 24-hour helpline dedicated to gambling problems in the country.</p>

